            . I am an officer. I have a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction - (read) - I was present in this Court when he was convicted, and know he is the man.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I had come out of the House of Correction that morning, after eight months' confinement, and not having drank any beer there, the spirits I took had got effect on me; I do not know what occurred.</p>
